      "writtenOn": "2015-09-24T07:35:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Actually, it\u0027s now part of ANSI C99, so we can use it :)\n\nSee for example http://www.dribin.org/dave/blog/archives/2010/05/15/c99_syntax/",
      "parentUuid": "2e2e2591_ebf85184",
